milestones.description: Carlisle and Sean Ervine's 202-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 187 between Grant Flower and Carlisle
Carlisle and Sean Ervine's 202-run partnership is ZIM's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 187 between Carlisle and Grant Flower
Grant Flower has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (214) for ZIM, going past Andy Flower

stories.title: Laxman seals a thriller
stories.subTitle: India v Zimbabwe, VB Series, 8th ODI, Adelaide
stories.summary: A record-breaking 202-run partnership between Stuart Carlisle and Sean Ervine went in vain as Zimbabwe fell just three runs short in a thrilling finish at the Adelaide Oval
